back\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zso1665702759701.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zso1665702759701.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zso1665702759701.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zso1665702759701\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters entity declarations in a DTD that contain the <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDATA</code> keyword.\n </p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104zso1665702759701_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"zso1665702759701__codeblock_k3j_sf4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation UNPARSEDENTITY\n  params\n     string Name: in\n     string PublicID: in\n     string SystemID: in\n     string Notation: in\n  endparams\n\nImplement your code here\n\nend; UNPARSEDENTITY operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zso1665702759701__section_wch_tf4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d90359e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zso1665702759701__ul_bc5_5f4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zso1665702759701__li_d48434e1_d48435e1_d48436e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Name</var>—name of the XML entity</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zso1665702759701__li_d48437e1_d48438e1_d48439e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">PublicID</var>—public identifier of the\n          XML entity</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zso1665702759701__li_d48440e1_d48441e1_d48442e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">SystemID</var>—local identifier of the\n          XML entity</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zso1665702759701__li_d48443e1_d48444e1_d48445e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Notation</var>—name of the notation\n          declaration</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zso1665702759701__section_m1c_wf4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d90359e85\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zso1665702759701__p_d137231e1_d137232e1_d137233e1\">XML streams can include references to data that does\n        not need to be processed by the parser, such as images, executables, files, or other data.\n        Instead, they are handled by another application or DTD, which is defined by a\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!NOTATION…</code> declaration.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zso1665702759701__p_d137234e1_d137235e1_d137236e1\">Data that does not need to be parsed is declared in\n        the DTD by an <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!ENTITY</code> declaration that includes the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDATA</code> keyword, followed by a reference to a\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!NOTATION…</code> declaration. This in turn points to the URI or application\n        responsible for holding or processing the unparsed data.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zso1665702759701__p_d137237e1_d137238e1_d137239e1\">When the parser encounters entity declarations\n        containing the <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDATA</code> keyword, it activates\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UNPARSEDENTITY</span> and passes the relevant details to resolve the notation\n        reference.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zso1665702759701__p_d137240e1_d137241e1_d137242e1\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104zso1665702759701_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"zso1665702759701__codeblock_cmb_yf4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;!ENTITY image SYSTEM “pic.jpg” NDATA JPG&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zso1665702759701__p_d137243e1_d137244e1_d137245e1\">This declaration causes the parser to issue the\n        following call to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UNPARSEDENTITY</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104zso1665702759701_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"zso1665702759701__codeblock_rps_yf4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">SaxCallHandler.UNPARSEDENTITY(\"image\", \"SYSTEM\", \"pic.jpg\", \"JPG\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zso1665702759701__p_d137246e1_d137247e1_d137248e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">JPG</code> after <code class=\"ph codeph\">NDATA</code>\n        is provided in <var class=\"keyword varname\">Notation</var>, and refers to a <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!NOTATION…</code>\n        DTD declaration.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534587\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534587\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UNPARSEDENTITY Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters entity declarations in a DTD that contain the NDATA keyword. Explain this code operation UNPARSEDENTITY params string Name: in string PublicID: in string SystemID: in string Notation: in endparams Implement your code here end; UNPARSEDENTITY operation Copy Parameters Name —name of the XML entity PublicID —public identifier of the XML entity SystemID —local identifier of the XML entity Notation —name of the notation declaration Description XML streams can include references to data that does not need to be processed by the parser, such as images, executables, files, or other data. Instead, they are handled by another application or DTD, which is defined by a <!NOTATION… declaration. Data that does not need to be parsed is declared in the DTD by an <!ENTITY declaration that includes the NDATA keyword, followed by a reference to a <!NOTATION… declaration. This in turn points to the URI or application responsible for holding or processing the unparsed data. When the parser encounters entity declarations containing the NDATA keyword, it activates UNPARSEDENTITY and passes the relevant details to resolve the notation reference. For example: Explain this code <!ENTITY image SYSTEM “pic.jpg” NDATA JPG> Copy This declaration causes the parser to issue the following call to UNPARSEDENTITY : Explain this code SaxCallHandler.UNPARSEDENTITY(\"image\", \"SYSTEM\", \"pic.jpg\", \"JPG\") Copy The JPG after NDATA is provided in Notation , and refers to a <!NOTATION… DTD declaration. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}